# CalculiX Docker image

An CalculiX image which is mainly designed to execute CalculiX jobs.

# Usage

Executing an CalculiX case from the current directory:
```bash
cd path/to/case/dir
docker container run -it --rm -v $PWD:/data tefe/calculix cgx parameters   
```

Get a bash:
```bash
docker container run -it --rm -v $PWD:/data tefe/openfoam bash    
```

**Notice**

You can change ```$PWD``` to any directory or environment variable that contains the case files.


